Subject: EPP server is not accessible
Description: we are trying to setup EPP server on hyper V but it is giving error when we try to access the console form the ip
What_We_Know__c:
- the server UI is not accessible

14.04 
- only 1 network adapter was added
- the console was accessible after adding the 2nd one
Solution_Comment__c:
we found that only 1 network adapter was added, and EPP requires 2 in order to work correctly.
After we added the 2nd one, the console was accessible.
